{"tid":1763123,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"泰國警察和中國公安破門而入，在曼谷拘捕中國異見人士","createTime":"2019-11-30T05:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T10:30:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":336,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9e5c0343cba194104a4415777fa9cf377be932","tid":1763123,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2019/1128/20191128095724123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2019%2F1128%2F20191128095724123.jpg&h=4c945952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在泰國取得聯合國難民身份的中國異見人士邢鑒，在其曼谷住所內，被十多名泰國和中國警方人員帶走，目前羈押在曼谷監獄。正在曼谷的難民柳學紅披露，邢鑒被捕時在電話中說，泰國警察和中國公安破門而入。有自稱來自中國江蘇的六名便衣公安聲稱持有拘留令，指邢鑒涉嫌在網上散布謠言，要泰國警察協助抓人。據稱，公安在其住所搜查了兩個多小時才離開。<br />\n<br />\n邢鑒曾經是「六四天網」義工，曾因「尋釁滋事罪」被拘，於2015年到泰國，向聯合國申請難民身份。其父親邢望力是中國維權人士，曾多次入獄被獄警毆打。<br />\n<br />\n中國公安越境到泰國抓人早有先例。2015年10月，有瑞典國籍的香港銅鑼灣書店股東桂民海，在泰國芭提雅一住所被中國便衣人員綁架回國，至今仍然在囚。"},{"pid":"54099905ea64bb088f0897e2e22fdfcc52fbe939","tid":1763123,"uid":22675,"like":191,"dislike":2,"score":189,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"泰國不嬲奶共 華為cctv 仲有高鐵"},{"pid":"0a4696ba292217892feb643d42fc89704563c5ca","tid":1763123,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:43:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/xing-11272019065445.html?encoding=traditional\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fxing-11272019065445.html%3Fencoding%3Dtraditional&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=272bb803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/xing-11272019065445.html?encoding=traditional</a>"},{"pid":"9994f679245b7e01098301c453dba7798180c5af","tid":1763123,"uid":21545,"like":168,"dislike":1,"score":167,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國泰族自治區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eede06d49